== Picture Jumps

[#picjumps-2over1]
=== Two-over-one auctions

:picbid1: https://bridgewinners.com/article/view/21-auctions-fast-arrival-vs-picture-bidding/
:picbid2: https://bridgewinners.com/article/view/more-about-picture-jumps-and-fast-arrival/
