=== Four-level agreement

When 4m is the first call that shows support for partner's minor
then, it is not minorwood.

The rules are the same as in three-level non-agreement except that
the bid is not a jump.  But it must still be between 4m and 4NT. + 

@ cheapest unbid-suit
@ fourth suit
@ opener's 2nd suit
@ responder's 2nd-suit

