=== Standard

We open one-major, they preempt
[nobr]#{tribull} 4NT = KC asking#

We open one-minor, they preempt +
[nobr]#{tribull} 4NT = take-out, {simto} 4{xtimes}m + 6{xtimes}om#

We overcall @ 1-level, they preempt +
[nobr]#{tribull} 4NT = take-out#

=== Other Suggestions

&Mike Lawrence&

We overcall two-minor, they preempt
[nobr]#{tribull} 4NT = plain aces#

&Eric Greco &

We act, they preempt: +
_If partner has shown five or more, except for 1-level overcalls, then
4NT is KC asking._

